events.name: Cloud Study Jams 2019
events.description:
Want to get started on the Google Cloud, but don't know where to begin? Or maybe you missed our first session?
Join us for our first Cloud Study Jam session! Together we'll work through three Google Cloud Platform Essentials labs, then you will get free access to the next quest so you can finish this series of labs at home to get a Google-hosted badge for your online profile. You will be able to get hands-on experience with Docker, Kubernetes and Scientific Data Processing, which will earn you additional badges.
Join this meetup to get an official Google training, a $70+ value, free of charge!

• What to bring
Bring a laptop (PC, Mac or Chromebook)! The labs will run on all of the latest versions of the popular browsers. For the best experience, make sure your laptop has Firefox or Chrome installed.

events.name: Assistant 2019 - Build Actions for Your Community
events.description:
Actions on Google and Google Assistant are one of the major Google technical areas and we want to invite the whole developer community to learn about creating Actions for the Google Assistant.

This is a 1-day event for developers of all skill level to come together to learn how to create Actions for Google Assistant. The event features a blend of tech talks, code labs, discussions, demos and networking.

events.description:
العالم الرقمي في متناول يديك
يوفّر برنامج "مهارات من Google" دورات تدريبية مرنة ومخصّصة لتزويدك بالمهارات الرقمية اللازمة لمساعدتك على تنمية مسارك الوظيفي أو نشاطك التجاري بالوتيرة التي تناسبك.

events.name: The Fundamentals of Digital Marketing
events.description:
Digital marketing is one of the most commonly used types of a marketing campaign in existence today; one of the reasons why that so has to do with the fact that so many people spend so much time on the Internet.
Digital marketing includes advertising on websites, content marketing, social media marketing and anything that you do within the digital space.

The basic fundamentals of digital marketing are:
Social Media Marketing (SMM)
Search Engine Optimization (SEO)
Content Marketing.
Pay-Per-Click (PPC) advertising.
E-mail marketing.

‎سنشاركك معكم اليوم المزيد حول "نظرية التحكم" من خلال تقديم أساسياتها المختلفة وإعطائكم شرحًا موجزًا ​​لكل منها ، دون الغوص في الرياضيات المعقدة (المخيفة) التي تنشأ في الواقع بشكل طبيعي ، سيكون هذا موجزا ومختصرا ، أود أن تكون هذه كمحادثة وأريدنا جميعًا الاستمتاع بها. نلتقي على الساعة 10:30 إن شاء الله 🔥🔥🤗

‎‏in this webinar, We will share with you more about the "control theory " by presenting its different essentials and giving you a brief explanation of each one, without diving into the (daunting) complex math that actually arises naturally, i would love this to be as a conversation and i want us all to
‎‏enjoy it. See you at 10:30 pm Inchallh 🔥🔥🤗

events.name: Graphic design basics and fundamental
events.description:
عشاااق الديزاين 😍😍 وينكم؟! سهرتنا راح تكون خصيصا للناس الي تحب التصميم الجرافيكي و مهتمة انها تتعلموا وتبدا خطواتها فيه ،اليوم مع المتحدث "Benkhattou Feriel" راح نتعلموا أساسيات التصميم الجرافيكي وماهي القواعد والمفاهيم الأساسية لتعلم التصميم الجرافيكي ... موضوعنا راح نتطرقو ليه في حصتين اليوم وغدوة 😆 بزاااف راح نتعلموا جديد 🔥🔥خلوكم معانا كما عودناكم على 10:30pm .. هيا بارطاجيو مع صحابكم خلو يستفادوا معانا تاني 😉😉
__________________

‏" How to be a designer?"
‏" How to master design softwares ?"
‏these are the most common questions asked Nowadays in the field of Graphic Design
‏But are they the right questions to ask !
‏Actually No!
‏before you start learning anything in this life you need to begin with its basics and Fundamentals, same goes for Graphic design.
‏So instead of saying how to become a graphic designer you should be wondering what are the main rules and concepts of it ?
‏and that's what will " Benkhattou Feriel " Answer in her presentation under the title of " The basics and fundamentals of Graphic design".
